      "The 8-tier structure (100/500/1050/1600/2800/5900/12000/18500) started with FC 24 (Sept 2023)",
      "FC 24, FC 25, and FC 26 share identical USD pricing and tier structure",
      "EA Play subscribers receive 10% discount on all FC/FIFA Points purchases"
